org.cougaar.core.service.wp
Interface Callback

All Known Implementing Classes:
Response, Response.Bind, Response.Flush, Response.Get, Response.GetAll, Response.List, Response.Unbind
public interface Callback

A callback allowing asynchronous WhitePagesService interaction.

A client should keep the callback method as short as possible, since the WhitePagesService may use a single callback thread. See the ThreadService and SchedulerService for separate thread-handler options.
